What do you mean? Sausage is good.

11:11.719 --> 11:14.260
No. Hi, yes,
I'd like to order a large pizza, please.

11:21.954 --> 11:24.019
-Use your axe.
-Okay. Okay.

11:24.149 --> 11:25.524
Turn around and go and get him.

11:25.600 --> 11:27.942
Go, go, go... Die, you sucker.

11:28.002 --> 11:29.777
Okay, you got him.
Hit him again. Hit him again.

11:29.837 --> 11:31.222
-Go. Go.
-Again. Again.

11:31.283 --> 11:33.873
