don't you worry about that.

15:56.514 --> 15:58.379
-Listen, Mr. Cordell, I...
-Please.

15:58.899 --> 15:59.732
Call me Mark.

16:00.508 --> 16:01.528
Okay, Mark.

16:01.742 --> 16:02.517
-May I...
-Listen...

16:02.866 --> 16:04.077
May I call you Annie?

16:04.138 --> 16:05.807
