-The Teacher will protect me!

49:54.673 --> 49:58.629
Sure, you can put the Teacher in jail,
you can sizzle Louie Boffano,

49:59.078 --> 50:01.854
but what are you gonna do
about this drunken Rodney

50:01.914 --> 50:03.856
behind the wheel of this car?

50:03.955 --> 50:08.724
I'm looking down this road and
it's just one big blur to me!

50:11.223 --> 50:13.132
But I think I see a boy on a bicycle

50:13.192 --> 50:16.132
who looks an awful lot to me like... Hey.

50:17.463 --> 50:18.674
Oh, God, no!

50:18.897 --> 50:20.728
No! Oh, God! Please no!

50:20.789 --> 50:22.540
-Who will protect you?
-Please, no!

50:22.601 --> 50:24.076
-The Teacher!
-Who will protect you?

50:24.136 --> 50:25.767
-The Teacher!
-Who will shield you?

50:25.828 --> 50:27.228
-Say, 'The Teacher!'
-The Teacher!

50:28.404 --> 50:30.480
-Say it, 'The Teacher will protect me!'
-The Teacher!

50:30.743 --> 50:33.910
-Say it! Again! Again! Again!
-The Teacher will protect me!

50:34.780 --> 50:35.474
No!

50:56.101 --> 50:56.970
Here.

51:02.121 --> 51:02.858
Oh.

51:09.315 --> 51:10.890
You can't let him drive like that!

51:11.887 --> 51:13.153
You're absolutely right, Annie.

51:14.148 --> 51:15.549
He could hurt somebody.

51:20.364 --> 51:20.995
No!

51:32.571 --> 51:34.011
Make sure she gets home safe, Eddie.

51:37.443 --> 51:38.390
Where you going?

51:50.208 --> 51:51.444
Why did he do that?

51:53.988 --> 51:55.092
'Cause you scared him.

51:55.668 --> 51:58.188
You don't ever wanna do that shit again
'cause he will hurt you.

52:00.312 --> 52:01.489
I don't wanna see you get hurt.

52:03.974 --> 52:05.674
You said you had a kid, right, captain?

52:06.472 --> 52:07.089
Eddie.

52:08.307 --> 52:09.260
My name is Eddie.

52:10.402 --> 52:11.948
Yeah, I got a daughter. 14.

52:14.546 --> 52:16.142
Why do you let him do these things?

52:19.351 --> 52:21.154
You got too many questions. Come on.

52:21.453 --> 52:22.514
Let's get out of here.

52:34.161 --> 52:34.911
Hey, Mom.

52:36.689 --> 52:38.501
Do you think we could
go to the mall later?

52:38.562 --> 52:39.176
No.

52:40.739 --> 52:41.693
Get some ice cream?

52:42.274 --> 52:42.886
No.

52:45.511 --> 52:47.751
