Why don't you finish your homework?

54:55.440 --> 54:56.614
He looks good.

54:56.675 --> 54:58.918
-You gonna examine me like that sometime?
-Oh, you wish.

54:58.979 --> 55:00.802
You're on call on Saturday night.

55:07.915 --> 55:09.235
You said he can be reasoned with.

55:13.800 --> 55:14.696
But he can't.

55:15.727 --> 55:16.538
What happened?

55:16.760 --> 55:18.470
We tried it your way, Juliet.

55:18.530 --> 55:19.834
And it didn't work out.

55:22.701 --> 55:23.909
Now, you've got to promise me

55:23.969 --> 55:25.788
that you're gonna stay out of our lives.

55:26.371 --> 55:27.857
And that's what Oliver wants, too?

55:28.445 --> 55:30.502
Well, Oliver thinks that
we should be heroes,

55:31.220 --> 55:31.947
but he's wrong.

55:33.809 --> 55:36.572
But he's promised to keep his mouth
shut so that's all that matters.

55:37.616 --> 55:39.187
And now you've got to promise, too.

55:39.312 --> 55:41.349
Promise you what?
I'm going to abandon you?

55:41.771 --> 55:44.360
That you're gonna keep your mouth
shut and stay out of our lives.

55:47.251 --> 55:48.407
It's my life, right?

55:48.827 --> 55:50.666
Isn't that what you said? My life, my kid?

55:55.000 --> 55:56.181
-Right?
-Yeah.

55:57.533 --> 55:58.288
Promise me.

56:03.845 --> 56:04.847
I promise you.

56:14.365 --> 56:15.271
Hey, Oliver.

56:16.650 --> 56:17.432
Hi, Annie.

56:22.427 --> 56:24.197
-Oliver...
-Puberty.

56:44.816 --> 56:45.538
Okay.

56:46.071 --> 56:47.043
'Guilty.'

56:47.886 --> 56:48.502
'Guilty.'

